### Erros ilustrativos (token placeholder; sem credenciais reais)
### 401 sem Authorization / 403 mismatch / 422 currency inválida
### 429: ver quickstart — sem body Problem garantido

### 401
POST https://sandbox.fiscalmod.bwb.pt/v1/documents
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: 22222222-2222-4222-8222-222222222222

{"external_id":"x","document_type":"invoice","currency":"AOA","issued_at":"2026-07-21T10:00:00+01:00","seller":{"tax_id":"FIXTURE-NIF-AO-0001","name":"S"},"lines":[{"line_id":"L1","description":"d","quantity":"1","unit_price":"1.00","tax_code":"NOR"}]}

###
### 403 FISCAL_SCOPE_MISMATCH (seller sintético diferente do scope)
POST https://sandbox.fiscalmod.bwb.pt/v1/documents
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: 33333333-3333-4333-8333-333333333333
Authorization: Bearer REPLACE_WITH_MODULE_SANDBOX_TOKEN

{"external_id":"mismatch-demo","document_type":"invoice","currency":"AOA","issued_at":"2026-07-21T10:00:00+01:00","seller":{"tax_id":"FIXTURE-NIF-OTHER-9999","name":"Other"},"lines":[{"line_id":"L1","description":"d","quantity":"1","unit_price":"1.00","tax_code":"NOR"}]}

